WITH PERFUME,

06:14.533 --> 06:15.834
AND ME WITH BILLY.

06:16.800 --> 06:18.500
OR BOBBY.

06:19.600 --> 06:20.900
YEAH, BOBBY.

06:20.967 --> 06:23.200
YEAH, IT WAS BOBBY.

06:23.266 --> 06:24.467
OR WAS IT BEN?

06:25.400 --> 06:26.700
OH, WHO KNOWS?

06:26.767 --> 06:29.734
ANYWAY, IT STARTED
WITH A "B."

06:31.967 --> 06:34.600
