06:34.667 --> 06:37.333
DID YOU HAVE...

06:43.900 --> 06:45.867
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

06:45.934 --> 06:47.734
WHY, MANY TIMES
THAT FIRST TIME.

06:47.800 --> 06:49.934
MANY, MANY TIMES!

06:51.000 --> 06:52.266
YOU DID?

06:52.333 --> 06:53.600
YOU DIDN'T?

06:53.667 --> 06:54.934
NO!

06:55.000 --> 06:57.734
OH, IT WAS NICE.

06:57.800 --> 06:59.734
BEING NEAR CHARLIE
WAS NICE,

06:59.800 --> 07:02.133
BUT IT WAS FIVE YEARS
BEFORE I KNEW

07:02.200 --> 07:04.433
WHAT MADE YOUR EYES
GO BACK IN YOUR HEAD.

07:09.367 --> 07:12.533
DOROTHY, DID YOU...

07:12.600 --> 07:14.367
HAVE...

07:14.433 --> 07:15.633
HOW COULD I?

07:15.700 --> 07:19.000
IT ALWAYS SEEMED TO HAPPEN
BEFORE I WAS IN THE ROOM.

07:22.133 --> 07:23.600
BLANCHE, YOU ARE OUT OF BED.

07:23.667 --> 07:24.867
THIS IS WONDERFUL.

07:24.934 --> 07:26.367
NO, IT IS NOT WONDERFUL.

07:26.433 --> 07:27.600
I WAS LYING IN BED EATING

07:27.667 --> 07:29.100
AND IF I DON'T GET
UP AND WALK AROUND

07:29.166 --> 07:30.900
I'M GONNA BECOME
AS BIG AS A HIPPO.

07:30.967 --> 07:32.834
AND LIFE, IF I CAN STILL
CALL IT THAT

07:32.900 --> 07:35.433
HAS TO GO ON IN ONE FORM
OR THE OTHER. SO HERE I AM.

07:35.500 --> 07:40.133
I'LL JUST SPEND MY REMAINING
YEARS IN THE COMPANY OF WOMEN.

07:40.200 --> 07:41.567
ONLY REASON I'M STICKING AROUND

07:41.633 --> 07:44.300
IS TO READ DANIELLE STEEL'S
NEXT BOOK.

07:44.367 --> 07:46.567
