HALFWAY THROUGH
THE CHEESECAKE

11:50.633 --> 11:52.567
AND HAVEN'T SOLVED
OUR PROBLEM.

11:52.633 --> 11:54.567
MAYBE WE CAN'T
SOLVE IT.

11:54.633 --> 11:57.800
MAYBE MA'S DOING
THE RIGHT THING BY LEAVING.

11:57.867 --> 12:00.600
YOUR BROTHER
IS SUCH A YUTZ!

12:00.667 --> 12:02.800
I JUST PHONED HIM,

12:02.867 --> 12:03.934
AND HE HAD
THE NERVE TO ASK

12:04.000 --> 12:06.166
WHAT'S FOR
DINNER TOMORROW.

12:06.233 --> 12:07.266
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

12:07.333 --> 12:09.467
HE SHOULD HAVE DINNER
WAITING FOR ME.

12:09.533 --> 12:14.233
NOT THAT I'M A FAN
OF SQUIRREL GUMBO.

12:14.300 --> 12:17.033
HOW DO YOU EXPECT
TO LIVE TOGETHER?

12:17.100 --> 12:18.467
