12:18.533 --> 12:19.934
AND ALREADY YOU'RE FIGHTING.

12:20.000 --> 12:22.166
WHAT, THIS IS <i>LITTLE</i>
<i>HOUSE ON THE PRAIRIE?</i>

12:22.233 --> 12:25.734
THERE ARE MORE FIGHTS HERE
THAN AT CAESAR'S PALACE.

12:27.333 --> 12:30.166
DOROTHY.

12:30.233 --> 12:32.500
WHERE'S
MY HEATING PAD?

12:32.567 --> 12:34.400
HOW SHOULD I KNOW?

12:34.467 --> 12:35.834
IF THIS ISN'T IT,

12:35.900 --> 12:37.367
WHAT OTHER
ELECTRICAL APPLIANCE

12:37.433 --> 12:39.867
ARE YOU USING
UNDER THAT BLANKET?

12:42.066 --> 12:43.367
THERE WE ARE, SOPHIA,

12:43.433 --> 12:44.867
THE PERFECT
AFTER-DINNER TREAT--

12:44.934 --> 12:47.400
A NICE DISH OF JELL-O.

12:47.467 --> 12:50.200
I HATE JELL-O.

12:50.266 --> 12:52.567
